𝗗𝗮𝘆 𝟯𝟰: 𝗞𝗲𝗲𝗽 𝗜𝘁 𝗦𝗶𝗺𝗽𝗹𝗲!
⚡ Simplicity is the key to agility! 
👉 Tip: Keep processes, communication, and workflows as simple as possible. Complexity slows things down.

💡 𝗗𝗮𝗶𝗹𝘆 𝘁𝗶𝗽𝘀 for Scrum Teams and especially Scrum Masters! Get practical advice, best practices, & strategies to boost collaboration and sprint success.
